This paper deals with learning representations of entities and relations in knowledge bases using neural embeddings, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the link prediction task, which is a common problem in databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper introduces a novel approach for rule extraction, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
